Class Description
Actor
This is the abstract class for all the objects in the game which includes the frog, background image scores and etc.
Animal
This is the class for the main character in the game which is the frog.
BackgroundImage
Add image into the game.
Digit
Represents the number character in the game.
End
Represents the home of the frog which is the 5 platforms above.
FroggerApplication
A separate class that contains the start function which is used by the launch function in main.
GameController
Controller of the game.
GameFactory
Factory of the game (FlyWeight Pattern).
GameModel
Model of the game.
GameView
View of the game.
HighScoreController
Controller of the High Score screen.
HighScoreFactory
Factory of the High Score Screen (FlyWeight Pattern).
HighScoreModel
Model of the High Score Screen Responsible for all the data needed to run High Score Screen.
HighScoreView
View of the High Score screen.
InfoController
Controller of the Info screen.
InfoFactory
Factory of the Info Screen (FlyWeight Pattern).
InfoModel
Model of the Info Screen Responsible for all the data needed to run Info Screen
InfoView
View of the info screen.
Log
Represents the log in the game which is one of the platform for the frog to stand on it without falling into the water.
Main
Responsible for launching the JavaFX
MainMenuController
Controller of the Main Menu screen.
MainMenuFactory
Factory of the Main Menu Screen (FlyWeight Pattern).
MainMenuModel
Model of the Main Menu Screen Responsible for all the data needed to run Main Menu Screen.
MainMenuView
View of the Main Menu screen.
MvcModel
Interface for all the models in Frogger.
MyStage
Background for the game .
Obstacle
Represent obstacles such as the truck and lorry which had to be avoided by the frog.
SceneManager
Manage scene between screens.
Testing
JUnit Testing
TimeCountdown
Represents the timer digit in the game.
Turtle
Represents the turtle in the game which is one of the platform for the frog to stand on it without falling into the water.
WetTurtle
Represents the wet turtle in the game which the frog had to jump out of the way before getting drown.
World
Layout panes for the game.
